2gp6ac: 8px 12px 8px 12px; background-color: rgb(128, 72, 245); border-radius: 100px; opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-17gd20u\" style=\"--extracted-r6o4lv: rgb(255, 255, 255); --framer-link-text-color: rgb(0, 153, 255); --framer-link-text-decoration: underline; transform: none; opacity: 1;\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-pk5f8l\" data-styles-preset=\"Epu0NqScc\" style=\"--framer-text-color:var(--extracted-r6o4lv, rgb(255, 255, 255))\">WooCommerce App</p></div></div></a><!--/$--></div></div></div></header></div></div></div></div><style data-framer-html-style=\"\">html body { background: rgb(245, 245, 245); }</style><div data-framer-root=\"\" class=\"framer-dUrVg framer-gUzfC framer-tVeiB framer-1jKPC framer-LWPyD framer-x5wcum\" style=\"min-height:100vh;width:auto;display:contents\"><div class=\"framer-17f3cyu\"><div class=\"framer-kzoqy1\" data-framer-name=\"FAQ\"><div class=\"framer-q3ylb8\" style=\"transform:none\" data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\"><h2 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1b3gxfz\" data-styles-preset=\"nBYoYjZot\">Verve AI – FAQ</h2><h3 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1a26qz\" data-styles-preset=\"vB4AUeX65\">How do I install Verve AI on Shopify?</h3><ol class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Visit the Verve AI app listing on the <!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"https://apps.shopify.com/verve-ai\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong class=\"framer-text\">Shopify App Store</strong></a><!--/$--></p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Click <strong class=\"framer-text\">“Add app”</strong> and approve the installation in your Shopify admin</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Once installed, Verve AI will automatically sync your products, variants, and order history</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">You can immediately start generating AI forecasts and reorder suggestions from the dashboard</p></li></ol><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">No manual setup required.</p><h3 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1a26qz\" data-styles-preset=\"vB4AUeX65\">How do I install Verve AI for WooCommerce?</h3><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">For WooCommerce merchants, Verve AI is installed as a WordPress plugin:</p><ol class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Visit our <!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/verve-ai-inventory-forecasting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wordpress Plugin</a><!--/$--> page.</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Install and activate the plugin, install</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Connect your store and approve access to your WooCommerce data</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Sign up for our 14 day free-trial</p></li></ol><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Once connected, Verve AI will sync your products, variants, and order history automatically.</p><h3 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1a26qz\" data-styles-preset=\"vB4AUeX65\">How do I sign up if I’m a WooCommerce merchant?</h3><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">WooCommerce merchants connect to our app directly from their Wordpress dashboard. Your Verve AI account and WooCommerce accounts are linked for security purposes.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Billing and account management are handled directly through Verve AI (not via WordPress or WooCommerce).</p><h3 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1a26qz\" data-styles-preset=\"vB4AUeX65\">How does billing work?</h3><ul class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><strong class=\"framer-text\">Shopify merchants:</strong><br class=\"framer-text\">Billing is handled through <strong class=\"framer-text\">Shopify Billing</strong>, so your subscription appears directly on your Shopify invoice. No separate payments or credit cards required.</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><strong class=\"framer-text\">WooCommerce merchants:</strong><br class=\"framer-text\">Billing is managed through your Verve AI account on our website. Your subscription renews automatically unless cancelled.</p></li></ul><h3 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1a26qz\" data-styles-preset=\"vB4AUeX65\">Can I cancel anytime?</h3><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Yes — absolutely.</p><ul class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><strong class=\"framer-text\">Shopify merchants:</strong><br class=\"framer-text\">You can cancel by uninstalling Verve AI from your Shopify admin. Once removed, billing stops automatically.</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\"><strong class=\"framer-text\">WooCommerce merchants:</strong><br class=\"framer-text\">You can cancel anytime from your Verve AI account dashboard. Your subscription will not renew after cancellation.</p></li></ul><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">There are no long-term contracts.</p><h3 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1a26qz\" data-styles-preset=\"vB4AUeX65\">What happens to my data if I uninstall or cancel?</h3><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">When you uninstall or cancel Verve AI:</p><ul class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Your store is securely disconnected</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Your account data is flagged for deletion</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">All data is permanently deleted within <strong class=\"framer-text\">30 days</strong> (or sooner upon request)</p></li></ul><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">For full details, please see our Privacy Policy.</p><h3 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1a26qz\" data-styles-preset=\"vB4AUeX65\">How accurate are the forecasts?</h3><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Forecast accuracy depends on factors such as:</p><ul class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\"><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">The amount and quality of your sales history</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Seasonality and demand volatility</p></li><li data-preset-tag=\"p\" class=\"framer-text\"><p class=\"framer-text\">Lead times and restock behaviour</p></li></ul><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Our models continuously learn from your store’s data and improve over time as more history is collected.</p><h3 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1a26qz\" data-styles-preset=\"vB4AUeX65\">Do I need technical skills to use Verve AI?</h3><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">No technical skills required.</p><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">Verve AI is designed to be <strong class=\"framer-text\">plug-and-play</strong> for both Shopify and WooCommerce merchants.<br class=\"framer-text\">Once installed and connected, everything runs automatically — no spreadsheets, no code, no manual configuration.</p><h3 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1a26qz\" data-styles-preset=\"vB4AUeX65\">How do I get support?</h3><p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-v6od6f\" data-styles-preset=\"ScpgnH6GX\">You can reach us anytime at <!--$--><a class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1veg3uv\" data-styles-preset=\"usLKCTepC\" href=\"mailto:hello@getverveai.com\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong class=\"framer-text\">hello@getverveai.com</strong></a><!--/$--><br class=\"framer-text\">We also actively use customer feedback to shape the product roadmap, especially during early access and beta phases.</p></div></div></div></div><div id=\"overlay\"></div><div class=\"framer-1h2kvss\"></div><div class=\"framer-lsv2fh\" data-framer-name=\"Footer\"><div class=\"ssr-variant hidden-v3h10d hidden-907ff8\"><div class=\"framer-ihe3tg-container\"><footer class=\"framer-qm2kR framer-98yyr framer-oXIyl framer-zKijR framer-LWPyD framer-qm5p50 framer-v-qm5p50\" data-framer-name=\"Desktop\" style=\"background-color: rgb(19, 33, 68); width: 100%; opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-15ufsj5\" data-framer-name=\"Inner\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-6ttnxu\" data-framer-name=\"List\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-1ofpdd9\" data-framer-name=\"Title\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><div class=\"framer-8wi8wv-container\" style=\"opacity: 1;\"><!--$--><a class=\"framer-uL3sp framer-1i9bryg framer-v-1i9bryg framer-1hend0p\" data-framer-name=\"Default\" style=\"height: 100%; width: