  "bodyText": "Home\n\nAbout\n\nContact\n\nShopify App\n\nWooCommerce App\n\nVerve AI – FAQ\nHow do I install Verve AI on Shopify?\n\nVisit the Verve AI app listing on the Shopify App Store\n\nClick “Add app” and approve the installation in your Shopify admin\n\nOnce installed, Verve AI will automatically sync your products, variants, and order history\n\nYou can immediately start generating AI forecasts and reorder suggestions from the dashboard\n\nNo manual setup required.\n\nHow do I install Verve AI for WooCommerce?\n\nFor WooCommerce merchants, Verve AI is installed as a WordPress plugin:\n\nVisit our Wordpress Plugin page.\n\nInstall and activate the plugin, install\n\nConnect your store and approve access to your WooCommerce data\n\nSign up for our 14 day free-trial\n\nOnce connected, Verve AI will sync your products, variants, and order history automatically.\n\nHow do I sign up if I’m a WooCommerce merchant?\n\nWooCommerce merchants connect to our app directly from their Wordpress dashboard. Your Verve AI account and WooCommerce accounts are linked for security purposes.\n\nBilling and account management are handled directly through Verve AI (not via WordPress or WooCommerce).\n\nHow does billing work?\n\nShopify merchants:\nBilling is handled through Shopify Billing, so your subscription appears directly on your Shopify invoice. No separate payments or credit cards required.\n\nWooCommerce merchants:\nBilling is managed through your Verve AI account on our website. Your subscription renews automatically unless cancelled.\n\nCan I cancel anytime?\n\nYes — absolutely.\n\nShopify merchants:\nYou can cancel by uninstalling Verve AI from your Shopify admin. Once removed, billing stops automatically.\n\nWooCommerce merchants:\nYou can cancel anytime from your Verve AI account dashboard. Your subscription will not renew after cancellation.\n\nThere are no long-term contracts.\n\nWhat happens to my data if I uninstall or cancel?\n\nWhen you uninstall or cancel Verve AI:\n\nYour store is securely disconnected\n\nYour account data is flagged for deletion\n\nAll data is permanently deleted within 30 days (or sooner upon request)\n\nFor full details, please see our Privacy Policy.\n\nHow accurate are the forecasts?\n\nForecast accuracy depends on factors such as:\n\nThe amount and quality of your sales history\n\nSeasonality and demand volatility\n\nLead times and restock behaviour\n\nOur models continuously learn from your store’s data and improve over time as more history is collected.\n\nDo I need technical skills to use Verve AI?\n\nNo technical skills required.\n\nVerve AI is designed to be plug-and-play for both Shopify and WooCommerce merchants.\nOnce installed and connected, everything runs automatically — no spreadsheets, no code, no manual configuration.\n\nHow do I get support?\n\nYou can reach us anytime at hello@getverveai.com\nWe also actively use customer feedback to shape the product roadmap, especially during early access and beta phases.\n\nAI Forecasting Software for E-Commerce Businesses\n\nQuick Links\n\nHome\n\nAbout\n\nPricing\n\nWhy Verve AI\n\nContact\n\nBlog\n\nTools\n\nImportant\n\nVerve AI Shopify\n\nVerve AI WooCommerce\n\nTwitter\n\nPrivacy Policy\n\nTerms\n\nFAQ\n\nGet in Touch\n\nHello@GetVerveAI.com\n\nCopyright © 2026 Verve AI. All rights reserved.",
